==Stages== *'''Panorama''' - The main stage of the festival. *'''Luna''' - A stage very similar to Panorama when it comes to size. *'''Juno''' - A smaller stage next to Panorama. *'''Sensation''' - This stage is the home of electronic dance music. *'''Pacific''' - A smaller music stage located inside a tent. *'''Norrköping Lounge''' - This stage is an indoor stand-up comedy stage.
