{{one source|date=July 2015}} {{third-party|date=July 2015}} {{Use dmy dates|date=February 2015}} {{Infobox magazine | name = Newsweek Serbia | image_file = | image_size = | image_caption = | publisher = Adria Media Group | language = [[Serbian language|Serbian]] | country = [[Serbia]] | based = [[Belgrade]] | founded = February, 2015 | firstdate = | finaldate = | category = [[News magazine]] and [[web portal]] | frequency = Weekly and daily | editor= [[Milorad Ivanović]] | editor_title = Editor-in-chief | website = {{URL|http://newsweek.rs/}} }} '''''Newsweek Serbia''''' is a weekly [[Serbian language]] [[news magazine]] and web portal published in [[Serbia]] as the Serbian edition of ''[[Newsweek]]''.
''Newsweek Serbia'' was established in 2015. The magazine and portal is owned by [[Adria Media Group]]. It has a neutral political stance. It is based in Belgrade. Magazine published weekly on Mondays, web portal post daily news. The [[editor-in-chief]] of the magazine is Milorad Ivanović, the editor-in-chief of the web portal is Andjela Popović.
